OL,3,CFormer Liverpool Mayor Joe Anderson
OL,4,Cappears in court accused of corruption
OL,6,FVideo report by Rob Smith
OL,8,FFormer mayor of Liverpool Joe Anderson
OL,9,Fhas appeared in court accused of
OL,10,Finvolvement in council corruption.
OL,12,FAnderson, 67, was one of 12 people
OL,13,Fcharged as part of Operation Aloft,
OL,14,Flaunched by police to look into the
OL,15,Fawarding of commercial and business
OL,16,Fcontracts from Liverpool City Council
OL,17,Fbetween 2010 and 2020.
