OL,3,CFormer Liverpool Mayor Joe Anderson
OL,4,Cappears in court accused of corruption
OL,6,FSpeaking outside of court following
OL,7,Fthe hearing, Anderson said he will
OL,8,Fcontinue to defend himself and clear
OL,9,Fhis name.
OL,11,FHe said: "I'm absolutely delighted
OL,12,Fthat we've now got to the stage where
OL,13,Fa crown court hearing will be heard
OL,14,Fwhere people can actually get to see
OL,15,Fall of the evidence and what I've been
OL,16,Faccused of.
OL,18,F"I've defended myself and protested my
OL,19,Finnocence from day one. I'll continue
OL,20,Fto do so because I've done nothing
OL,21,Fwrong.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
