OL,3,CFormer Liverpool Mayor Joe Anderson
OL,4,Cappears in court accused of corruption
OL,6,FAlso attending court was Derek Hatton,
OL,7,F77, who was deputy leader of Liverpool
OL,8,FCity Council in the 1980s, and a
OL,9,Fformer director and assistant director
OL,10,Fat the local authority.
OL,12,FHatton, of Aigburth, Liverpool, who
OL,13,Fwas part of Labour's militant faction
OL,14,Fin the 1980s, denied one count of
OL,15,Fbribery and one count of counselling
OL,16,For procuring misconduct in a public
OL,17,Foffice.
OL,19,FBefore he confirmed his name, age and
OL,20,Faddress, District Judge Wendy Lloyd
OL,21,Fasked Hatton not to chew in court.
