OL,6,FAdam McClean, 54, of Woolton, also
OL,7,Fentered the dock on a charge of
OL,8,Fconspiracy to bribery, to which he
OL,9,Fentered no plea.
OL,11,FOther defendants appeared at court
OL,12,Fremotely via videolink.
OL,14,FThe council's former head of
OL,15,Fregeneration Nick Kavanagh, 56, of
OL,16,FMossley Hill, Liverpool, indicated not
OL,17,Fguilty pleas to two counts of bribery.
OL,19,FPhillipa Cook, 49, of the same
OL,20,Faddress, also indicated not guilty
OL,21,Fpleas to two counts of bribery.
